811
00:41:58,099 --> 00:41:59,860
And that's exactly the problem.

812
00:42:00,320 --> 00:42:02,721
It's, the feature sits really deep.

813
00:42:03,201 --> 00:42:04,242
It's not part of the core.

814
00:42:04,282 --> 00:42:06,143
It's like five layers into the interface

815
00:42:06,203 --> 00:42:07,544
