816
00:42:07,584 --> 00:42:09,785
So that obviously didn't fix the core problem.

817
00:42:11,403 --> 00:42:12,844
I'm going to be really honest with you.

818
00:42:13,985 --> 00:42:15,767
We really didn't fix this.

819
00:42:16,167 --> 00:42:16,888
